Egyptian President  Hosni Mubarak  has
ordered the formation of a committee to amend some articles of
the constitution, Vice President  Omar Suleiman  said in a
televised speech today.  The committee will start its work today, he said. The
president also ordered the formation of a committee to
investigate violence in Tahrir square and relay its findings to
